Dialogue: 1,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是凯伦  蓝仙女
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.02,0:00:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm Karen, the Blue Fairy
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.30,0:00:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天这个故事特别没品
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:00:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this tale lacks class
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.40,0:01:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为这个故事就叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for it's the story of
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大灰狼海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.15,0:01:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"The Big Bad Bubble Bass"
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.47,0:01:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.47,0:01:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:16.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Evil
Dialogue: 1,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Rapturous day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的藏品今天就能集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Today my collection will be completed
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.68,0:01:29.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于  猪格伦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:29.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At long last, Pigulon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(428,892)}三小猪战队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(458,252)}战猪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:33.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1680,236)}仿生猪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1010,476)}预留位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:32.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,154)}猪格伦大促
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:32.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1126,694)}仅一天
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.12,0:01:31.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三小猪神力战队的首领
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:31.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,leader of the Swine Force 3 Action Team
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.87,0:01:33.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要到手了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:33.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得穿什么衣服我都想好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.80,0:01:35.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I know just what to wear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.03,0:01:43.29,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1432,852)}狼人小子
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看好了  狼人小子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Behold, Wolfman Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三小猪战队的死对头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,mortal enemy of the Swine Force 3
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(972,336)}玩具桶
Dialogue: 1,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几小时后  故事渐渐发展
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:01:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hours later, as the story goes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.27,0:02:02.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王整着衣服抵达了目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:02.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass arrived still adjusting his clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.43,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(782,346)}猪格伦大促
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.79,0:02:06.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sold out?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:09.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是很想抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.75,0:02:11.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not really?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:13.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了猪格伦  我的一生就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.17,0:02:17.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Without Pigulon my life is over
Dialogue: 1,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.81,0:02:21.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不敢相信我们买到最后一个猪格伦了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we got the very last Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.08,0:02:24.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.08,0:02:24.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赶快玩玩看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's play with him
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1072,380)}猪格伦
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不能瞎拆猪格伦的宝贝包装
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:34.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not Pigulon's precious packaging
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一下子就亏成半价了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.52,0:02:36.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes half his value
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,挠痒痒可真好用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a good scratcher
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一半又亏没了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.07,0:02:45.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There goes the other half
Dialogue: 1,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,实在忍不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This cannot stand
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.97,0:02:51.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须从那群傻子手中解放猪格伦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must liberate Pigulon
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,from the clutches of those buffoons
Dialogue: 1,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  先生们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:56.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, good sirs
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.35,0:03:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很难不注意到你们的猪格伦手办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.35,0:03:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but notice your Pigulon action figure
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能向你们买
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.97,0:03:01.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Might I buy
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,换
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:02.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,trade
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不就骗过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or swindle him from you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,归你了  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:06.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's all yours, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能为朋友干啥都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.32,0:03:07.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Anything for a friend
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.15,0:03:09.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.15,0:03:09.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想玩猪猪人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:12.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wanna play with the pig man
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它也是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:13.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's mine too
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.15,0:03:14.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.15,0:03:14.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,猪格伦是我跟派大星一起出钱买的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.77,0:03:18.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and I both chipped in to buy Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welp, see you later
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我以宅神的名义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:25.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,By the gods of nerd-dom
Dialogue: 1,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要抢到那个猪格伦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.17,0:03:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I will acquire that Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无论付出什么代价
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:29.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No matter what
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,于是海霸王谋划着  鼓起勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:33.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So Bubble Bass plotted, his courage he'd found
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自顾自地大声咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as he ranted and raved with no one around
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我消失  破铜烂铁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:38.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be gone, vile machine
Dialogue: 1,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有玩具等着我去救
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:40.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have a toy to rescue
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  神秘陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, mysterious stranger
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要我帮什么忙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How may I help you?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是玩具检查员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.02,0:03:49.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Toy Inspector
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.89,0:03:53.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须把从你家搜查到的危险玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take any dangerous toys
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,found on your premises
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带回局里审问
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:55.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,back to the station for questioning
Dialogue: 1,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,危险玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dangerous toys?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快进来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:00.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You better come in right away
Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.22,0:04:09.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  你把你那一点点玩具放哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, now where do you keep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:09.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your meager allotment of playthings?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在保险库里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:10.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Over here in the vault
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保险库
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vault?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开始检查吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's start, shall we?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有不少玩具都得检查呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got a lot of toys to get through
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,幸好我按字母顺序都排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:34.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I alphabetized them
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是食蚁兽艾伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Aaron Aardvark
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.12,0:04:40.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.12,0:04:40.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是食蚁兽艾比
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Abbie Aardvark
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:45.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is she dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.62,0:04:48.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是食蚁兽艾伯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Albert Aardvark
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全得很
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:52.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:04:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1005)}检查了不少玩具后
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来检查P
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.52,0:04:58.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on to the Ps
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是猪神猪格伦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:00.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Porktastic Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.67,0:05:01.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.27,0:05:03.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:03.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的非常危
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's very dang--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,顺序搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:06.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I went out of order
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是高危帕西瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is Perilous Percival
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个危险吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is he dangerous?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.47,0:05:23.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是世界知名猎鬼师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.12,0:05:25.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a world-famous ghost hunter
Dialogue: 1,0:05:25.20,0:05:29.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我检测到你家出现大规模闹鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I've detected a massive haunting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,occurring within your domicile
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须把你家扫描一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to scan your home
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找出被附身的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.80,0:05:34.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to pinpoint the possessed item
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼魂活动还挺多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lots of ghost activity
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There is?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.67,0:05:46.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这件物品内含恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.42,0:05:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This item contains a malevolent spirit
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧  猪格伦中招了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, not Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须将其带回实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll have to take him back to the lab
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把恶鬼遏制住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.56,0:05:55.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for spectral containment
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不必
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:57.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No need
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  我们马上就在这替你驱鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:06:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we'll banish that ghost for you right here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.47,0:06:18.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁这么大胆  敢把我驱离这个境界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:18.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who dares banish me from this plane?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是他起的头
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He started it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.93,0:06:22.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:22.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, no
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,耶  猪格伦得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.97,0:06:28.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yay, Pigulon is saved
Dialogue: 1,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.97,0:06:37.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ScumBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,屁大星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:38.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Putrick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这群大白痴快把猪格伦交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:41.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You blithering fools better hand over Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我大喝特喝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.70,0:06:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll chug, and I'll glug
Dialogue: 1,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打嗝把你家吹塌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.15,0:06:46.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll belch your house down
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:49.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody's home
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.03,0:06:55.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来喝大泡弹打嗝燃料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:55.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Time for some Fizz Bomb burp fuel
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.51,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(928,690)}大泡弹
Dialogue: 1,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说  快把猪格伦交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.20,0:07:14.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said hand over Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.77,0:07:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不然我大喝特喝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,or I'll chug, and I'll glug
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打嗝把你家吹塌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:19.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll belch your house down
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二遍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.52,0:07:20.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Again
Dialogue: 1,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你好运
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.35,0:07:26.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我用石头造的这个石头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:26.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I built this rock entirely out of rock
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,638)}火山辣酱
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来加加热吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:33.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's turn up the heat
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这石头不是按传统方法做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.45,0:07:43.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They just don't make rocks the way they used to
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.30,0:07:45.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:45.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:46.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放我们进去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.47,0:07:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let us in
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.02,0:07:47.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼章鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.02,0:07:47.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squid, Squid
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.40,0:07:47.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:47.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on
Dialogue: 1,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:48.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not interested
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没兴趣三个字  你们哪个字听不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:58.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What part of "not interested" don't you understand?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:00.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.45,0:08:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要在你家取走那个猪格伦娃娃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need that Pigulon doll
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,within your residence
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说了没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I said not interested
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我大喝特喝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:11.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then I'll chug, and I'll glug
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打嗝把你家也一块吹塌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:14.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and I'll belch your house down too
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.30,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,332)}大泡弹可乐
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我搞不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't understand
Dialogue: 1,0:08:41.52,0:08:45.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打这么多嗝  早该把他家变臭气了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those burps should have rendered his home
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,into stinky vapors
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:47.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.95,0:08:51.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给我家做了防海绵宝宝处理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:51.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just had my house SpongeBob-proofed
Dialogue: 1,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的打嗝计划失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With his belching now foiled
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只剩下一个计划
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.62,0:09:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he had but one plan
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.05,0:09:09.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑回家找妈妈  男儿泪轻弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:09.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,run home to his mommy and cry like a man
Dialogue: 1,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他泪如泉涌  向他妈撒了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:13.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wept like a fountain and lied to the ma'am
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说那些男生是坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those boys were the bullies
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而他是他妈的可爱小羊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:19.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he her sweet lamb
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他妈暴怒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His mother was livid
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,她尖叫  她吐唾沫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:24.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,She screamed, and she spat
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.35,0:09:28.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对不让坏蛋抢她儿子玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.35,0:09:28.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No villain should take her son's toy like that
Dialogue: 1,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am so disappointed
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.89,0:09:40.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你打嗝早该到高一的水平了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:40.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You should be belching at a tenth-grade level by now
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让老妈给你示范怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let Mama show you how it's done
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Mother
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那玩意我用不着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.96,0:09:46.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't need that stuff
Dialogue: 1,0:10:05.90,0:10:10.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们快把我家海霸王玩具还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.90,0:10:10.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You boys had better give my Bubble Bass his toy back
Dialogue: 1,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可  玩具是我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.27,0:10:13.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,B--but it's our toy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还有小票
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.37,0:10:14.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have the receipt
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.65,0:10:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老妈  那收据肯定是伪造的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,M-M-Mama, th-th-that receipt must be a forgery
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要  老妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, Mama
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:29.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to--
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:38.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't cry
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们有东西可以让你振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got something that might cheer you up
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:44.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟派大星要把猪格伦给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:46.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick and I want you to have Pigulon
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Joy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gimme, gimme, gimme
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:51.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你一定会爱上的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know you'll love him
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把玩得特开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:58.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We sure had fun playing with him
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.38,0:11:09.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王自诩获胜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:09.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Bubble Bass won, so he told himself
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.50,0:11:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跑回家把他的新娃娃放上了架
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.50,0:11:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as he ran home to put his new doll on the shelf
Dialogue: 1,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥被迫独自一人重建自己家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:18.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward was forced to rebuild alone
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他的保险并不赔付
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,His insurance won't cover
Dialogue: 1,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被打嗝吹塌的住房损失
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.32,0:11:22.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,belch damage to home
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都是你童话故事害的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Your fairy tale did this
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:26.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get outta here
Dialogue: 1,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各位再会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:28.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Farewell
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下次讲故事再见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Until next story time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.00,起司 一般标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H00FF97&}海底厌绵社
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(697.802,374)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:37.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(711.802,668)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:41.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1530,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(771.802,666)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:38.92,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(631.802,464)}指导总监
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.38,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(743.802,534)}统筹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(565.802,506)}联合监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28.71\pos(659.802,540)}监制
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.01,0:11:43.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1468.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们玩得可开心了  垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had some good times, Trashy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过你一定会爱上垃圾场的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But you're gonna love the dump
Dialogue: 1,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还能交到不少垃圾新朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:52.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll make so many trashy new friends
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会想你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.00,0:12:01.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna miss you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡芙老师好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My mistake
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海霸王好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.71,0:12:13.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员先生好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mr. Mailman
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都不在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得戴眼镜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:18.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Maybe I need glasses
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵受害者同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.43,0:12:31.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fellow sponge sufferers
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第413届厌绵社大会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.45,0:12:35.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the 431st We Hate SpongeBob Club
Dialogue: 1,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在正式开始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will now come to order
Dialogue: 1,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们的社训是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now our motto
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.37,0:12:42.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们对海绵宝宝没有恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:42.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We don't mean SpongeBob any harm
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是单纯受不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:45.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just can't stand him
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁愿意分享
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.77,0:12:47.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any
Dialogue: 1,0:12:47.44,0:12:50.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝害你们新吃的苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.44,0:12:50.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,new sponge-pain they would like to share?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你吃了多少次苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How much time do you have?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I do
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.41,0:12:52.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可想分享了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:52.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, I do
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要拆开装满我苦头的包裹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.94,0:12:54.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to unwrap my package of pain
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,分享先慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.47,0:12:57.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold that agony
Dialogue: 1,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Proceed
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有受的苦要分享
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:04.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have some misfortune to share
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,主席有请受害者泡芙发言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:07.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The chair recognizes sufferer Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请取发言海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please receive the Speaking Sponge
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是上周的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:13.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It all began last week
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当时我还在享受我最爱的事之一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:17.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was enjoying one of my favorite things
Dialogue: 1,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给同学颁发驾照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:21.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,awarding a student their driver's license
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:21.07,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1334,256)}滑浪学校
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你通过了驾考  贝尔蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've passed your driver's exam, Bertie
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.40,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,242)}裤头村驾照
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.52,0:13:26.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Congratulations
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没了你我肯定考不过  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I couldn't have done it without you, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.17,0:13:32.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你肯定人人都能教得会
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:32.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bet you can teach anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几乎算是人人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost anyone
Dialogue: 1,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,驾照不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:40.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice license
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能摸摸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I touch it?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.60,0:13:44.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gross
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.80,0:13:52.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子你好像有空啊  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:50.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like you have an opening
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:52.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in your schedule, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想走
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to leave
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但大家都知道  没人能逃得掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we all know there is no escape from
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全加速进入车流
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.55,0:14:12.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Accelerate safely into traffic
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在来三百六十度回旋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now for a 360-point turn
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:22.17,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,626)}停
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差点闯停车标志牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almost ran a stop sign
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝毁了我美丽的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob destroyed my beautiful school
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟上周一个样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:38.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just like last week
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.35,0:14:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我们陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here for you
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁想接下去分享的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who would like to share next?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.14,0:14:47.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I would
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我想分享抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'd like to share a hug
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来得让你跺上邮票了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.12,0:14:52.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like you could use a stamp
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.11,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,814)}秘鲁收
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.10,0:14:57.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接下来该轮到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:57.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I believe that I am next in the roundelay
Dialogue: 1,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我发言海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:15:00.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My speaking sponge, please
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来在蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was at the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想在第一餐和第二餐间隙吃顿点心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:07.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to grab a light snack between first and second lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上菜了  尊贵的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Order up, oh, valued customer
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.05,0:15:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我饥饿的胃总算有了寄托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally sustenance for my starving stomach
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.89,0:15:17.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope it's perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:23.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太油了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's too greasy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这根薯条也不够油
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:30.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And this fry isn't greasy enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管我想吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:33.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Try as I might--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.57,0:15:37.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝一点卡路里都不让我摄入
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:37.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob would not let me consume a single calorie
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.55,0:15:41.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来想喝点汽水解解渴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:41.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tried to take a sip of soda to slake my thirst
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,泡不够多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not fizzy enough
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个浑身是洞的浑蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That perforated pest
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是一口蟹黄堡都不让我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.29,0:15:58.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wouldn't let me taste a morsel of Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我蟹黄堡还来  吹毛求疵的臭海绵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me back my patty, you festering fusspot
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:05.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,芝麻排得不整齐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:10.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The sesame seeds are misaligned
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生菜起了太多皱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.90,0:16:12.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the lettuce has too many wrinkles
Dialogue: 1,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,番茄失去了光泽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:15.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The tomato has lost its sheen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快让我吃东西  可恶的妨碍者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.19,0:16:19.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me eat, you insufferable interrupter
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.45,0:16:24.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Victory is mine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点海绵味  不过还行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.85,0:16:40.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A tad spongy, but not bad
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.57,0:16:45.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个煎炸厨师害我得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.57,0:16:45.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That fry cook has given me a slight case of
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,消化不良
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.75,0:16:48.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,indigestion
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.91,0:16:58.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝不能让客人吃到不完美的蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:58.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I shall let no customer eat a less-than-perfect patty
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,忘戴帽子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I forgot my hat
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.90,0:17:13.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个白痴害我肚脐都打结了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:13.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That squishy simpleton left my navel in knots
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这也叫吃尽苦头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:18.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You call that suffering?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你们讲个真正可怕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.07,0:17:21.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you a truly terrifying tale
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是一个黑夜  海绵四处出没
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.35,0:17:24.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was a dark and spongy night
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:24.93,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(962,692)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我静静在实验室里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was working peacefully in my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,研究最新发明来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on my newest invention to, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,帮助鱼类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:32.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help fishkind?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:33.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我的恐怖厕纸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:37.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, my terrible toilet paper
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会把裤头村从海底抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,will wipe Bikini Bottom off the face of the ocean
Dialogue: 1,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,纸里还加了衬芯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plus it's quilted
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为什么老是有东西害我没法好好奸笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why does something always ruin a good evil laugh?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就在那时  我看到了它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:03.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But then I saw it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有只野生的海绵宝宝进入了我实验室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:08.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wild SpongeBob had gotten into my lab
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凯伦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Karen
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,它又进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It got in again
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你窗户又忘关了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:16.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you leave the window open again?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跑进我主机里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's in my mainframe
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你个坏鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.68,0:18:27.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You dirty bird
Dialogue: 1,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.12,0:18:28.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get down from there
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.25,0:18:28.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.25,0:18:28.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Git
Dialogue: 1,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  懒骨头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Lazybones
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把它扫到门外去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:40.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sweep it out the door
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他把我们都锁外面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:01.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's locked us out
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以要是听到了海绵宝宝的可怕声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So if you hear that horrible sound of a SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.82,0:19:12.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.82,0:19:12.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just run
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃命要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Run for your lives
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家淡定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.05,0:19:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Calm down
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我空调又出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:21.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My AC is just acting up again
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢海神王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:25.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank Neptune
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这样就吃尽苦头了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.62,0:19:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You think you all have it bad?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.27,0:19:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着听我实时发生的海绵恐怖故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:30.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait until you hear my tale
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.19,0:19:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of spongy terror in real time
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,三
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:35.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Three
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.62,0:19:36.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:36.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,two
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:37.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,one
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He had arrived
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是门外却没人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But there was no one there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能的确无事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it was nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.90,0:19:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会不会海绵宝宝已经早就进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or was SpongeBob already in the house?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能借杯盐水吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:56.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I borrow a cup of saltwater?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:19:59.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.15,0:20:06.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  盐水只是妄图不请自来的借口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:03.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, the saltwater was just a ruse
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to come inside uninvited
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们在开派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:09.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you having a party?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝自然而然地抓紧时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:12.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Naturally, SpongeBob lost no time
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把房里所有人都烦一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:14.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,annoying everyone in the room
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:16.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等不及要上下一节课了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait until my next lesson
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,邮递员  不得不说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.77,0:20:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mailman, I gotta tell ya
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你送来的每一件包裹都是特别快递
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every package from you is a special delivery
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后再见  好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:27.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's catch up soon, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,样子还挺健康  海霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:29.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looking fit, Bubble Bass
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最近是不是在举重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Been pumping the iron, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有痞老板  有没有人跟你说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:35.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And, Plankton, has anyone ever told you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你的眼睛最可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you have the loveliest eye?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.00,0:20:41.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然  如果海绵宝宝就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.00,0:20:41.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, if SpongeBob was around
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那他的粉红尖头朋友也不会远到哪去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.05,0:20:45.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,his pointy pink pal couldn't be far behind
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你家潘趣酒没了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.90,0:20:49.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're out of punch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.56,0:20:51.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会再调一批特制菠萝潘趣酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.75,0:20:54.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll mix up a batch of my special pineapple punch
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,手工家常制作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.82,0:20:57.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's homemade
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用我家墙壁做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.60,0:20:59.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Made out of the walls of my home
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,凡是没有海绵宝宝搞破坏的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:09.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And no SpongeBob story would be complete
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是不完整的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.02,0:21:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without him destroying something
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,菠萝潘趣酒来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:13.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got pineapple punch
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,讲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:30.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The end
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.07,0:21:37.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们现在得去哪继续开社内大会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:37.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where are we gonna finish our club meeting now?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.68,0:21:41.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我知道有地方可以让你们继续开会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:41.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know a place you could have your meeting
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁准备好要吃餐前点心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:48.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's ready for hors d'oeuvres?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.61,0:21:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,牙签
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.15,0:21:53.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toothpicks
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们发言海绵都用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're all out of speaking sponges
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,才没用光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, you're not
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还剩一个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.62,0:22:00.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's one left
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.68,0:22:05.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后我就
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:05.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I was
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咳他邮件咳了好几个星期
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.17,0:22:08.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Coughing up his mail for weeks
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.23,0:22:16.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I declare
Dialogue: 1,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本次厌绵社大会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.20,0:22:19.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this meeting of the We Hate SpongeBob Club
Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,休会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.07,0:22:21.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,adjourned
